full_text: .@Health_Affairs: "News Media Reporting On Medication Treatment For Opioid Use Disorder Amid The Opioid Epidemic." https://t.co/nCnGW3xrsZ via @AndisRobeznieks

.@JohnsHopkinsSPH study about news coverage of opioid use disorder (OUD) meds found that it increased substantially in 2015 and 2016 compared to the prior eight years. However, most coverage has not noted the significant underuse of this type of treatment. https://t.co/NKxxkAiWU6

Underuse of an evidence based practice is not being highlighted enough in the media...
